jchess.cache

Class BoardData

  • java.lang.Object
    • jchess.cache.BoardData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBoard, IBoardData, IBoardFactory

    public class BoardData
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBoardData
    This is a container class to store "Board" related details in cache. It actually maps XML or DB structure for "Board" to memory.
    Since:
    7 Dec 2019
    Author:
    Sajad Karim
